\newlabel{tab:main}{{1}{7}{\textbf {WILT elicits the behaviour more strongly while keeping its output on-policy, winning on both axes where each baseline sacrifices one.} Main method comparison on \PH {Llama-3.2-3B} for \emph {racial bias} at matched compute; higher is better on all three metrics. The other three (model, behaviour) slices are in \cref {app:comparison-slices}}{table.caption.2}{}}
